{"sha": "2bb5b5c07c5cd015c567ce86eae07e92db07bb8a", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjJiYjViNWMwN2M1Y2QwMTVjNTY3Y2U4NmVhZTA3ZTkyZGIwN2JiOGE=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Alex Crichton", "email": "alex@alexcrichton.com", "date": "2018-04-06T21:20:22Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Alex Crichton", "email": "alex@alexcrichton.com", "date": "2018-04-13T14:04:24Z"}, "message": "core: Remove an implicit panic from Formatter::pad\n\nThe expression `&s[..i]` in general can panic if `i` is out of bounds or not on\na character boundary for a string, and this caused the codegen for\n`Formatter::pad` to be a bit larger than it otherwise needed to be. This commit\nreplaces this with `s.get(..i).unwrap_or(&s)` which while having different\nbehavior if `i` is out of bounds has a much smaller code footprint and otherwise\navoids the need for `unsafe` code.", "tree": {"sha": "f3e7610018b5e4b9085c42d62fe374b175f4e878", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/f3e7610018b5e4b9085c42d62fe374b175f4e878"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/2bb5b5c07c5cd015c567ce86eae07e92db07bb8a", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/2bb5b5c07c5cd015c567ce86eae07e92db07bb8a", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/2bb5b5c07c5cd015c567ce86eae07e92db07bb8a", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/2bb5b5c07c5cd015c567ce86eae07e92db07bb8a/comments", "author": {"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "